          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1611576451866-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Peruvian-style king prawn & rice chowder</strong> topped with the<strong> halved sweetcorn cobettes </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
